The '''Auşeu-Borod Corugea Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Bihor County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 26 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.financiarul.com/articol_48670/italienii-de-la-alerion-ridica-o-ferma-eoliana-in-bihor-.html Italienii de la Alerion ridica o ferma eoliana in Bihor {{ro}}] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110720013143/http://www.financiarul.com/articol_48670/italienii-de-la-alerion-ridica-o-ferma-eoliana-in-bihor-.html |date=July 20, 2011 }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 2.5 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] each, which will deliver up to 65 [[Megawatt|MW]] of power, enough to power over 25,700 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately €85 million.

